---
// src/pages/projects/brand-identity.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Brand Identity | NEXUS Case Study">
  <article class="case-study">
    <h1>Brand Identity & Systems</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Foundation, visual language, and consistency.</p>

    <section class="overview">
      <h2>The Challenge</h2>
      <p>Transforming complex organizational needs into cohesive visual systems that scale across digital and physical environments.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="process">
      <h2>Strategic Approach</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Research:</strong> Auditing existing market positioning.</li>
        <li><strong>Systematization:</strong> Developing modular design tokens.</li>
        <li><strong>Implementation:</strong> Defining guidelines for corporate identity and stationery.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="featured-work">
      <h2>Featured Clients</h2>
      <p>Ascendant Group, Amathemba, At Home Vet Care, Chameleon, Dudu-Bervely, and more.</p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>